Product name: Vintage M. I. Hummel Music Box, Danbury Mint Collectible, Goebel Decor, Signed Numbered, Home Decor, Office Decor, Musical Decor
Description:
This Vintage Music Box would be a wonderful addition to add to your collection of music boxes, home decor, Goebel collection, Danbury Mint Collection, and office decor.  It plays the tune of "Merry Wanderer" and is from the M. I. Hummel Music Box Collection by Danbury Mint.  On the top, it has a Hummel scene of a little boy walking along a gravelled path, with a satchel in his hand, and a cross in the background behind him.  All around the side of the box is a pastoral scene with green grass and trees.  On both the sides and the top is a beautiful blue sky.  The top lid shows the registered trademark name of "M. J. Hummel."  When the lid is removed, you see the inside bottom covered with a dark green velvet type fabric.  The musical winding key is inside the box.  The bottom of the box is stamped with "Merry Wanderer from the M. I. Hummel Music Box Collection by the Danbury Mint".  The wording goes on to state "Edition of 90 firing days, with the Music Box number of B6917 written in gilt gold.  Below that is the Hummel and M. I. Description:
Soft, comfortable, protective leather thimble conforms to the shape of your finger for easier sewing! You HAVE to try this if you have a medical condition which causes circulation problems or sensitive fingertips. Also perfect if you frequently sew, are a quilter, professional framer (for sewing down projects such as needlework, jerseys, shirts, etc...) Thumb sizes as well.(custom sizes available- Measure the circumference of your finger ABOVE the knuckle for sizing.) Thimble should be snug at first because it will stretch to mold to your finger size.
PLEASE BE SURE TO SPECIFY SIZE WHEN ORDERING!!!!
Here are the directions for determining sizing:
 Measure the circumference of your finger ABOVE the knuckle for sizing. Take a piece of string/yarn and wrap it (not too tightly) AROUND your finger ABOVE your middle knuckle to find the circumference and measure the string. It should be between 2 and 2 3/4 inches long. (2 would be SMALL, 2 1/4 MED, 2 1/2 LARGE) I can also make X-SMALL and X-LARGE if needed! Thimble should be snug at first because it will stretch to mold to your finger size.
Please contact me for special requirements or custom sizing. Also sold individually.

Product name: Steampunk Neck Corset - Shoulder Armor - womens armor - Fantasy Armor - Steampunk Pauldron - Shoulder Armour - larp armor - spike epaulettes
Description:
A one of a kind steampunk neck corset or shoulder armour jewelry that is feminine yet fierce! It features rusted thorns and wire mesh roses, no one is going to mess with you wearing this baby! 
'Thorn' is a play on the idea of what we think of as 'floral' or 'feminine' and instead celebrates the rose thorns, and the strength of women.
This piece would make a perfect decorative ladies pauldron for an amazing costume. Beware though, although this will make you look like a bad mama jama, it is purely decorative and unlikely to deflect melee attacks. 
I created this originally for a jewelry competition in a floral category - but me being me - I really wanted to push the boundaries with what is considered floral, and what is considered jewelry. Two of my points of inspiration for this piece were the dark queen in the movie 'Mirror Mask' and the costumes in Mad Max.
The neck corset was designed for comfort, so I have not made it too thick as to choke the neck. It is boned and lined on the back, so you wont see any of the stitching for the beadwork. It has rusted found objects, thorns that have been treated with rust paint and sealed, and many wire mesh roses along the black vine that swirls around the design.
This piece is part of the Rust and Ruin Collection
Features:
- Handmade one of a kind design and beadwork, hundreds of hand sewn beads
- Comfortable design and adjustable 
- Boning included to keep the shape around the neck
- Lined on the back
- Hundreds of hours of beadwork
- Comes in a beautifully packaged jewelled gift box
- Ready to ship
*Please note that due to the elements used in the piece, it should not be washed, only spot cleaned.
